      "writtenOn": "2015-11-10T22:01:45Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "finger_pickBox is a QComboBox. QComboBox allows associating arbitrary data with its items. I suggest the following:\n\n* don\u0027t add any items to it in Qt Designed\n* in initFinger, use QComboBox::addItem to populate the combo box with items. Use this: http://doc.qt.io/qt-5.5/qcombobox.html#addItem (the second argument will be the data you want to associate with the given item)\n* in on_finger_touchButton_pressed, use QComboBox::currentData to get the data associated with the currently selected finger",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 33,
        "startChar": 4,
        "endLine": 37,
        "endChar": 5
      },
